## Services & Scope

**Required Services:**  
- Hospital-accredited bulk laundry services for all hospital linens and specialty healthcare items.
- Must provide all labor, transportation, equipment, tools, supplies, training, management, and administration.
- Performance in strict compliance with current Joint Commission (TJC) standards.

**Scope Flags:**  
- Non-personal services (no direct patient care)
- Contractor must meet specific Army & hospital regulations and standards.
- Must comply with DoD and Joint Commission (TJC) compliance throughout contract.

**Business Categories:**  
- NAICS: 812332 (Industrial Launderers)
- Small Business Size Standard: $47M
- PSC: S209 (Housekeeping/Laundry/Drycleaning)
- All business sizes encouraged to respond, identifying size in response.

